        <num>CCP 3152</num>
        <heading>3152.  Security of provisional administrator</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 3152.  Security of provisional administrator
The person appointed provisional administrator shall furnish security for the faithful performance of his duties in an amount determined by the court as being adequate for the protection of the heirs, legatees, surviving spouse in community, and creditors of the succession.</p>
        </content>
